{
  "stem": "5758.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because to jump the gun a little bit, when I went back after the war to find that girl, apparently soon after I left, she disappeared.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, when they started-- the Germans started torturing me and hitting me in the face, I said, look.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will want to know about my resistance group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would want to know names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm not prepared to give names under, under torture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to the Gestapo, I said, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was hiding up in the hills, up in the hill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and really, I have nothing to do with, with the resistance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody gave me a false identification paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I paid for it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is-- they put me in jail, checked with the-- with Vienna, with Austria, to see whether this is correct.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And naturally, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took me by, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by a prisoners' van to near Paris, to Drancy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Drancy was approximately [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] just outside Paris, in the suburbs of Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We arrived in Drancy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was actually like a block of flats, quite many rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had mattresses on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were many-- 50, 60 people in each hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] organized by Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was administered by Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the French were guarding the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we got food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were told that from time to time, they are taking people to work in Germany, away, away from France to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is what will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
